  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to libcddb</title>

    <para>
      The <application>libcddb</application> is a library that implements
      the different protocols (CDDBP, HTTP, SMTP) to access data on a CDDB
      server.
    </para>

    &lfs91_checked;

